{
  "name": "Santi Leads (contact + newsletter)",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "santi-leads",
        "responseMode": "responseNode",
        "options": {
          "allowedOrigins": "*"
        }
      },
      "id": "webhook-leads",
      "name": "Leads Webhook",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        260,
        300
      ],
      "webhookId": "santi-leads"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "respondWith": "json",
        "responseBody": "={{ { \"ok\": true } }}",
        "options": {
          "responseHeaders": {
            "entries": [
              {
                "name": "Access-Control-Allow-Origin",
                "value": "*"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "id": "respond-leads",
      "name": "Respond OK",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        760,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Add your lead handling here\n\nInsert nodes BETWEEN the Webhook and Respond (e.g. an **IF / Switch** on `{{$json.body.type}}` = `contact` vs `newsletter`, then **Send Email** to santi@santi.co.za, **Google Sheets \u2192 Append**, Slack, your CRM, etc.).\n\nIncoming JSON is under `{{$json.body}}`:\n- contact: type, name, email, phone, subject, message, page, submittedAt\n- newsletter: type, email, page, submittedAt",
        "height": 320,
        "width": 420
      },
      "id": "note-leads",
      "name": "Setup note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        240,
        480
      ]
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Leads Webhook": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Respond OK",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    }
  },
  "settings": {
    "executionOrder": "v1"
  },
  "active": false
}